## ðŸš€ Advanced Features

### Conditional Fields
```typescript
// Show different fields based on values
const createFields = useMemo(() => {
  const baseFields = [
    { key: 'name', label: 'Name', type: 'text', required: true }
  ];
  
  if (selectedType === 'PROJECT') {
    baseFields.push({
      key: 'deadline',
      label: 'Deadline',
      type: 'date'
    });
  }
  
  return baseFields;
}, [selectedType]);
```

